# CHANGELOG
 
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).
 
## [0.1.0] - 2021-06-03
 
### Added
- Script to open font desciptor files directly in Glyphs!
- Example .afontjson files
 
### Changed
- Refactored Python script across multiple modules
- Changes to .ajsonfile format. You will need to resave any converted fonts to adopt the new format.
    - Removed kerning and spacing data for monospaced fonts
    - Bitmap data is now a single array of strings
 
### Fixed
- Updated Node.js and Python scripts to support monospaced fonts
 
## [0.0.1] - 2021-06-21
  
Initial release.
 
### Added
 
- Node scripts to convert Amiga font contents and descriptor files to JSON data (.afontjson)
- Glyphs script to open .afontjson files
- Example Amiga fonts
